{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/4_PLAYER_CO-OP.jpg?t=1726593056\" /><br><br>Hellcome is a challenging and exciting <strong>survival party game</strong> in which, players must battle their way through hordes of zombies and other hellish creatures in order to survive. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/Hellcome_01__1_.gif?t=1726593056\" /><br><br>You'll control various characters, each with their own unique abilities. And more playable characters and enemies are coming soon!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Multiplayer COOP Mode: </h2> You can team up with friends to take on the challenges of the game together. Work together to complete objectives, defeat bosses, and survive as long as possible. <br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/ezgif.com-optimize__1_.gif?t=1726593056\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Intense and Challenging Gameplay: </h2>Despite the lighthearted visuals, there's <strong>no auto-aim to make things easier!</strong> You'll need to rely on your own skills and reflexes to take down the zombie hordes.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/ezgif.com-optimize__2_.gif?t=1726593056\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Unlock New Abilities and Builds:</h2> Experiment with different combinations to find the ones that work best for you. With a big bunch of abilities to choose from, there's always something new to discover.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/Select_Gif.gif?t=1726593056\" /><br><br>Hellcome is a thrilling and challenging game that's perfect for players who love roguelite games, bullet hell shooters, and cooperative multiplayer experiences.<br><br><img clas